Class BayesianNetworkSampler

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.utils.BayesianNetworkSampler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AmidstOptionsHandler, Serializable

    public class BayesianNetworkSampler
extends Object
implements AmidstOptionsHandler, Serializable
    This class implements the interface AmidstOptionsHandler. It defines a sampler of data from a BayesianNetwork.
